py to be performed in, Melissa, 56, admitted thatshe \\\"did not find that with any of the leotards.\\\"\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Rivers\", \"score\": 0.5885334446482907, \"rank\": 0.6940448558503234, \"text\": \"Melissa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Rivers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Rivers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a handful\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 378}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnasts' outfits\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"thatshe\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"the leotards\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think they are getting a little skimpier in the back.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if my a- looked like that, I would have no problem with it,\\\" she continued before acknowledging that the gymnasts were not the only athletes that faced the concern regarding their uniforms.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my a-\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"no problem\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnasts\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"the only athletes\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"the concern\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"their uniforms\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After noting that the swimmers' bathing suits were also questioned, Melissa says that the swimmers' situation is \\\"different\\\" because their swimsuits are \\\"meant to be aerodynamic.\\\"\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Rivers\", \"score\": 0.5885334446482907, \"rank\": 0.6940448558503234, \"text\": \"Melissa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Rivers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Rivers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the swimmers' bathing suits\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimmers' situation\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"their swimsuits\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do think that that was a little much,\\\" she said about the artistic swimmers, adding that some of their swimsuits were so small that they seemed to have \\\"Brazilian bottoms.\\\"\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the artistic swimmers\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"their swimsuits\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"Brazilian bottoms\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Melissa continued, \\\"I know [for] the divers, the bathing suits are getting really small for the men and the women.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Rivers\", \"score\": 0.5885334446482907, \"rank\": 0.6940448558503234, \"text\": \"Melissa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Rivers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Rivers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the divers\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"the bathing suits\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are mostly seeing that in the back, I am finding.\\\"\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 13